      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercially validated CFD solver with documented QA procedures meets MRL 2 requirement of Level 1.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R1 is a commercially released solver subject to vendor QA. Release notes and verification test suite documentation confirm Level 1 compliance. No custom solver modifications were introduced for this study."
