      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, use of published multi-laboratory dataset with documented sample preparation procedures is sufficient; detailed sample characterisation not required.",
      "rationale": "Experimental data sourced from the FDA interlaboratory study (Hariharan et al. 2011), which involved multiple independent laboratories and is considered the reference benchmark dataset for CFD hemolysis validation. Sample preparation and measurement protocols are fully documented in the published study. Not assessed as a separate factor per MRL 2 scoping."
    },
    {
