    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 MRL 2 guidance. CFD predictions of hemolysis index are validated against the FDA interlaboratory benchmark dataset with mean absolute error within inter-laboratory variability. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied across all five operating points. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support regulatory submission for the Class II CPB device.",
